{
  "stem": "1736.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's an unfortunate situation, but it's true, nevertheless.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So she had taken it upon herself to particularly look after, or give preference, to those children.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not exclusively, but anyway.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were put in touch with 10 other young children, the youngest of whom was six years old.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His parents had been taken to a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The only person he had left was an uncle in Tel Aviv, and the kid was by himself.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he was given-- we were taking charge of him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Where was he from?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't-- he was German, but I don't remember where.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, he told us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were told by these people that he had told them and--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The aim was to-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The aim was to get him to-- to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So here we are in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We're given a time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We're told, now, this and this is what you do, and what you do is you try and make your way to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In Vienna, you will be met by somebody who will guide you further.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then that's what took place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we left Berlin.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, only for maybe a week.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It wasn't even a week.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was about four days.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- my mother was at the station.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We said goodbye, and we left there together with an adult lady who accompanied us to Vienna with her daughter.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I'm not quite sure.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was sort of a chaperone, if you like.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we were really told beforehand, yes, she's your chaperone.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Listen to her, you know, if you can.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "On the other hand, remember you're on your own.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was given to all of us.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
